* Desmonus shook out her wing as Bloodystrike got off of it, noticing it's 
sore joints as she saw him reach out a hand to help her up.
She's just about to take it when suddenly the base rocks, luckely she was 
still on the ground. But she braces herself.

But then at Reptilicas report that they were merged again she slowly gets to 
her feet, hanging onto the wall for support just in case the base decided to 
shake again.
Though, Desmonus turnes her amber optics towards Reptilica.*

" But why did we have to relocate in the first place. I thought that we had 
already chosen our landing spot the last time we set down?"

* Desmonus steps away from the wall a bit, but keeping a bit close to it 
just to make sure she had something to support her if something else 
happened.
She began to dust off her armor and her wings, looking behind to make sure 
there weren't any smudges on her rear.
Nothing.
Desmonus looked towards Bloodystrike as he turned his gaze towards her.
But glad that at least it was the drink he was after at the moment.*

" Sounds good to me. Hmm...what would you recommend?"
